==Trivia== Today, his descendants form one of the biggest clans of the [[House of Yi]]. In addition, it is believed that the plaque on the [[Namdaemun]] was personally written by him.<ref>[http://100.naver.com/ Naver Encyclopedia], "[http://100.naver.com/100.nhn?docid=109130 양녕대군 [讓寧大君, 1394~1462<nowiki>]</nowiki>]", [[Naver]]"</ref>
He was an ancestor of [[Syngman Rhee]], Korean independence activist and the first [[Presidents of South Korea|South Korean president]].
