'''Sim Euigyeom''' (1535–1587) was a [[Korea]]n [[Joseon Dynasty]] politician, writer, and [[Neo-Confucianism|Neo-Confucian]] scholar. He was the head of the [[Westerners (Korean political faction)|Westerner]] political faction.

